    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >力智之王是一款独特的4X战略游戏，让你沉浸式体验中世纪的世界，提供以角色为中心新颖的叙事体验，结合角色扮演元素，令玩家恋恋不舍，渴望“再来一局”。借助封臣的力量，征服土地并赐予财富，提拔忠诚者，驱逐反抗者。召集领主参加史诗般的战斗，或派遣他们去冒险。夺取传奇宝物，凭借智慧和力量，确立你的统治地位。塑造贵族的特质，平衡他们的需求，使他们和你持有同样的战略目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切准备就绪，你可以在皇家森林策马奔腾，策划与外国统治者秘密结盟，在宏伟城堡里举行穷奢极侈的宴会等，只要你巩固了自身的统治地位。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/4ad42d77be808e128f27f7087e44151d.poster.avif?t=1740386871\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/4ad42d77be808e128f27f7087e44151d.webm?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/4ad42d77be808e128f27f7087e44151d.mp4?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精心打造封建王国</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/95f8854b48a46109799e9a3a292f5304.poster.avif?t=1740386871\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/95f8854b48a46109799e9a3a292f5304.webm?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/95f8854b48a46109799e9a3a292f5304.mp4?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细心选择你的封臣，他们效忠于你，换取封号、土地和权力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  掌控他们在地图上的行踪，在宫廷给他们安排职位，分派最契合角色特征的任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >封臣天性好斗，性格怪异。虽然你宽容大度，但你的封臣可能会惹是生非，引起内战，邻里争吵等问题。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>指挥封臣</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/60d4f62df1cc9255f487a600b99e7a69.poster.avif?t=1740386871\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/60d4f62df1cc9255f487a600b99e7a69.webm?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/60d4f62df1cc9255f487a600b99e7a69.mp4?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凶残贪婪的骑士，抑或是勤奋富裕的贵族？每个国王和封臣拥有独一无二的性格和特征，这会影响将来的合作、选择以及游戏风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成任务，为每个角色创造别具一格的故事，积累经验，提升角色等级，增强技能与特征。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色与他遇见的任何一个角色产生关联，良好的关系会推进外交进程，而糟糕的关系会造成混乱。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>参加和主办即时活动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/94486ad5860563b7740872e90e534d07.poster.avif?t=1740386871\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/94486ad5860563b7740872e90e534d07.webm?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/94486ad5860563b7740872e90e534d07.mp4?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主办和参加实时宴会、狩猎、地牢探险等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与封臣同醉，参加骑马比武等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在其后的游戏设置中，亲身感受这些活动的影响，记住，一切行为皆有后果。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开拓王国</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/d02493d39f8d337a4edf0bca03cdfd03.poster.avif?t=1740386871\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/d02493d39f8d337a4edf0bca03cdfd03.webm?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/d02493d39f8d337a4edf0bca03cdfd03.mp4?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在可视化城市视图中营造建筑物，解锁新的单位、物品等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 改善城市周围的土地，收集稀缺资源。夺取土地，分派给封臣，获得相对于其他帝国的战略性优势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >征服地图上的区域，但务必谨慎管理与其他帝国的关系，避免全面战争。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发动战争，参加决斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/8ab3017593529b9f5d0106f38b61cb86.poster.avif?t=1740386871\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/8ab3017593529b9f5d0106f38b61cb86.webm?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503170/extras/8ab3017593529b9f5d0106f38b61cb86.mp4?t=1740386871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参加个人决斗，解决贵族间的纠纷。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发动大规模战争，指挥部队，围攻城堡，征服敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创建地图和游戏模组</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建自定义地图和场景，打造真正（几乎）无限通关而扣人心弦的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为希望更深入体验的玩家提供模组支持。创建自己的帝国，添加新单位类型，或者设定全新的历史时期。</p></li></ul>",
